The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 BCCI ratings launched

Mumbai: The BCCI on Thursday launched its official ratings for international and domestic cricket, including women and juniors, but preferred to keep the prize money on offer a secret till close to the planned annual awards ceremony in April. The ratings would be updated regularly on the website www.bcciratings.com from October. 

The awards will be given in the following categories: 

Main categories Best Test and ODI batsman, bowler, fielder and allrounder; Best Test and ODI opening batsman; Most consistent/reliable Test and ODI player; Best Test and ODI innings of the year. 

Popular categories Test and ODI player of the year; My favourite player; Most stylish player; Master blaster of the year 

Viewers categories Player of the week and My favourite player. 

 (PTI) 




